After making an appearance at Essence festival, the cast of power via Starz dropped the trailer for the sixth and final season of Power which has been tagged “The Final Betrayal”. The series has enjoyed an interesting run and comes Courtney of A. Kemp and 50 Cent, who makes his directorial debut this season.
In the trailer, Ghost (Omari Hardwick) is trying to atone for the sins of his past by making a better tomorrow but unfortunately, old habits die hard. Everyone seems to be going after Ghost, who may have run out of options.
The trailer definitely highlights what should be a captivating season and thrilling end to the series. Power will return for Season 6 on August 25th 2019. Watch official trailer for ‘Power Season 6’ via YouTube below; 